      "parameters": {
        "content": "## üìä PostgreSQL Database Schema\n\n**Table: meme_posts**\n\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE meme_posts (\n  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n  template_id VARCHAR(50),\n  topic VARCHAR(100),\n  text0 VARCHAR(255),\n  text1 VARCHAR(255),\n  meme_url TEXT,\n  instagram_id VARCHAR(100),\n  posted_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW(),\n  success BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE\n);\n```\n\n**Usage:**\n- Auto-created on first run\n- Tracks last 7 days of posts\n- Prevents duplicate content\n- Logs failures for debugging\n\n**Why Not Store Binary?**\n- Meme images are hosted externally\n- Only store URLs (TEXT field)\n- Saves PostgreSQL storage quota\n- Faster queries\n- No bandwidth costs\n\n**Query Stats:**\n- Each run: 2 queries (SELECT + INSERT)\n- Query time: < 50ms each\n- Minimal CPU usage\n- Perfect for Eco Dyno",
